channel.title: Need original weapon skins + MP5 muzzleflash
channel.description:
(Damn I hope I posted this in the right section) So, I usually make back ups for most of the games I use mods on. Not Black Mesa, though. And that was dumb of me. I know. This thread wouldn't even exist if I had been a little more careful. But yeah, as you might've figured, I messed up some files. Yes, I would reinstall BMS but my internet has not been too kind lately, and I also have several custom files I would like to keep.
Sorry for the annoyance, but yeah, if anyone could upload the original weapon skins (and the muzzleflash for the MP5, as I got a really bland one that came with a skin), I'd be very happy!
Thanks for your time, and sorry in advance.
